name: .NET_MicroservicesDemo
description: This project is a demo for a mini system based on microservice architecture. The following steps have been taken in this project: • Building two .NET Microservices using the REST API pattern • Working with dedicated persistence layers for both services • Deploying our services to Kubernetes cluster • Employing the API Gateway pattern to route to our services • Building Synchronous messaging between services (HTTP & gRPC) • Building Asynchronous messaging between services using an Event Bus (RabbitMQ)
